observations.recommendation:
We recommended that the Management: 

Direct the Municipal Accountant to record the purchases of supplies, materials and other inventory items that qualify as part of inventory to the appropriate inventory account;

Require the Municipal Treasurer to prepare and submit the SSMI together with the supporting RIS to the Municipal Accountant for the recognition of the expense;

Recognize the undistributed goods and medicines for distribution under the appropriate inventory account; and

Require the Inventory Committee to include the physical count of all types of inventories in their activities and submit the required RPCI.
